WEBVTT

00:03.700 --> 00:05.500
Anyone thinking we know fuck all
about owt,

00:05.501 --> 00:07.500
needs to watch their back.

00:07.501 --> 00:09.499
So you've had your Labour,
reclassifying skunk,

00:09.500 --> 00:11.299
sending prices sky-high,

00:11.300 --> 00:15.818
literally, literally
taking the grass from its own roots!

00:15.820 --> 00:18.059
Now you've got your ConDemNation,

00:18.060 --> 00:21.419
Liberals noshing Tories
like altar boys picking dimps up!

00:21.420 --> 00:23.779
Have we had
a national fucking stroke...

00:23.780 --> 00:25.220
or what?!

00:25.221 --> 00:27.899
Is revolution a word...

00:27.900 --> 00:29.539
or was it never?

00:29.540 --> 00:31.659
Anybody watching needs to know,

00:31.660 --> 00:35.059
we cope better than average
with irony in Chatsworth.

00:35.060 --> 00:36.300
Well, for fuck's sake,

00:36.301 --> 00:37.899
we live in Manchester,

00:37.900 --> 00:41.179
and they charge us for water!

00:41.180 --> 00:44.179
I wandered lonely as a clown,

00:44.180 --> 00:45.940
necking mushrooms rarely found.

00:45.941 --> 00:48.419
This green and pleasant land

00:48.420 --> 00:50.259
in ancient times...

00:50.260 --> 00:52.259
yak yak yak yak yak yak yak yak yak!

00:52.260 --> 00:54.340
It's not theirs any more.

00:55.700 --> 00:59.139
This is our England now.

00:59.140 --> 01:00.260
Partaaaay!

01:05.740 --> 01:08.220
'Get a few quid, shag a few birds,
decent clobber,

01:08.221 --> 01:10.339
'smart motor. What then?

01:10.340 --> 01:14.339
'25% of lads aged 18-26
are waiting to be discovered.

01:14.340 --> 01:17.899
'And 50% of 16-year-olds
want to be famous.

01:17.900 --> 01:19.059
'For what?

01:19.060 --> 01:21.458
'Don't you need to be able to
do something first?

01:21.459 --> 01:23.780
'When the painful truth hits them hard
in the bollocks, there's going to be

01:23.781 --> 01:26.899
'plenty of disillusioned young men
and women out there.'

01:26.900 --> 01:28.700
There, son, go on.

01:30.420 --> 01:31.740
Go on, son. Ta!

01:31.741 --> 01:35.139
'It's handy for the alcohol companies
and drug dealers,

01:35.140 --> 01:37.458
'as everyone gets twatted to try
and deal with it.

01:37.459 --> 01:39.860
'Are you one of them bitter losers
wondering what went wrong?

01:39.861 --> 01:43.580
'Or is there still time
to do something about it?'

