around here again...

19:41.280 --> 19:44.080
I'll let this pit bull
get medieval on your arse.

19:49.640 --> 19:51.599
At least it's working.

19:51.600 --> 19:54.119
It's mint.
Might get one on my next upgrade.

19:54.120 --> 19:55.840
Thought you just got a new phone?

19:55.841 --> 20:00.879
30 quid. They're 150 in the shop ...
contract only.

20:00.880 --> 20:01.959
Who off?

20:01.960 --> 20:02.640
Daz Mitchell.

20:02.641 --> 20:05.159
You shouldn't even know him.

20:05.160 --> 20:08.039
It's all right for you to
shag his sister, though?!

20:08.040 --> 20:10.119
And a lovely girl she is, too.

20:10.120 --> 20:10.920
Hypocrite.

20:13.080 --> 20:15.759
Where's he even getting 30 quid?

20:15.760 --> 20:17.240
You should be
praising his initiative.

20:17.241 --> 20:19.239
Should be on a curfew.

20:19.240 --> 20:21.519
That's right. 24/7. Thought Police.

20:21.520 --> 20:24.839
Tight rein does them
no favours round here.

20:24.840 --> 20:27.000
Just enough slack
to stretch to Strangeways...?

20:27.001 --> 20:30.879
Social worker in the area... Is your
new mate getting under your skin?

20:30.880 --> 20:31.600
Behave.

20:31.601 --> 20:35.679
No, no ... careful Carl. Y'know,
enemy within. Cameron's Stasi...

20:35.680 --> 20:37.319
You should lay off the weed.

20:37.320 --> 20:38.678
It's got nothing to...

20:38.679 --> 20:39.600
THUMPING MUSIC IN EARPHONES

20:39.601 --> 20:42.559
INAUDIBLE

20:42.560 --> 20:44.399
Go on.

20:44.400 --> 20:45.720
It will pass, you know.

20:45.721 --> 20:47.239
What will?

20:47.240 --> 20:48.678
Thinking you're better.

20:48.679 --> 20:49.760
I'm going for a run.

20:49.761 --> 20:54.199
You not think there was plenty of
times I'd had enough of the gaff?

20:54.200 --> 20:57.559
I was a young man once,
sick of this place.

20:57.560 --> 21:01.479
But we ... Gallaghers ...
thrive in this environment.

21:01.480 --> 21:04.959
Darwinian. We're naturals when
it comes to playing the game.

21:04.960 --> 21:06.319
Their game...

21:06.320 --> 21:08.879
So how come everyone
else got off? Fiona, Lip...?

21:08.880 --> 21:14.239
Monica's snide little genes blagged
it to the front with them.

21:14.240 --> 21:18.839
Truth be told, they're not
made for it the same way.

21:18.840 --> 21:22.919
You and me... peas in a pod.

21:22.920 --> 21:26.799
Like your new bird said ... there's
more of me in you than the others.

21:26.800 --> 21:30.079
You're even better than I ever was.

21:30.080 --> 21:33.919
Running errands for Jamie,
plenty of readies.

21:33.920 --> 21:36.720
You're a proper success story.

21:38.480 --> 21:40.880
You can run but you can't hide.

21:54.080 --> 21:55.559
SHOUTING

21:55.560 --> 21:57.279
Someone help!

21:57.280 --> 21:58.360
Gallagher.

21:58.361 --> 22:01.519
Someone give me a hand! Someone!

22:01.520 --> 22:03.240
Gallagher!

22:14.320 --> 22:17.399
Been a while since we last
ate as a family.

22:17.400 --> 22:21.039
Sardine butties and Greggs'
custard slices for Cilla's birthday.

22:21.040 --> 22:24.919
A proper meal. Conversation.
We still need to clear the air.

22:24.920 --> 22:27.719
And you need some decent
scran inside you.

22:27.720 --> 22:30.199
Nerves, excitement, whatever it is...

22:30.200 --> 22:31.200
AIDS?

22:36.400 --> 22:38.159
Where's Kelly?

22:38.160 --> 22:40.999
Getting rifled off a six ft stud
with an eight inch length?

22:41.000 --> 22:43.359
Stop winding him up!

22:43.360 --> 22:46.519
I don't want him
wasting away before we get hitched.

22:46.520 --> 22:48.120
No one be late.

22:51.920 --> 22:53.479
Has he packed?

22:53.480 --> 22:54.720
Mam's had us too busy.

22:54.721 --> 22:56.879
Be around for her once he's gone.

22:56.880 --> 22:59.119
She's gonna need looking after.

22:59.120 --> 23:00.799
Still say we cut him up...

23:00.800 --> 23:03.399
I used to melt in Monica's eyes...

23:03.400 --> 23:05.120
but these...

23:06.400 --> 23:08.400
It better not turn all to mush.

23:11.160 --> 23:12.679
They'll sort that out.

23:12.680 --> 23:14.319
No wonder I'm mad for Carl.

23:14.320 --> 23:17.159
He obviously learnt his lyrics
from a master craftsman.

23:17.160 --> 23:20.479
Oh, eh up, here he is.

23:20.480 --> 23:21.879
Careful what you say.

23:21.880 --> 23:24.278
Eh, I've got someone to look
after me anyway.

23:24.279 --> 23:25.240
It was for football!

23:25.241 --> 23:26.799
Have you seen this?

23:26.800 --> 23:29.359
Another busy fucker
sticking their nose in.

23:29.360 --> 23:31.840
Some pensioner just naused
a brothel.

23:31.841 --> 23:33.559
It stopped people traffickers.

23:33.560 --> 23:34.520
