in there!

23:34.521 --> 23:36.319
See!

23:36.320 --> 23:37.759
Priorities... messed up.

23:37.760 --> 23:40.759
Converting to the dark side already.

23:40.760 --> 23:41.878
Don't be stupid!

23:41.879 --> 23:43.320
Got to earn a living somehow.

23:43.321 --> 23:46.079
Jamie. We're late.

23:46.080 --> 23:48.079
So are we.

23:48.080 --> 23:51.640
Don't know what the rush is.
KFC's 24/7.

23:53.640 --> 23:55.239
Cheers, everyone.

23:55.240 --> 23:57.039
Cheers!

23:57.040 --> 23:58.879
TIMER RINGS

23:58.880 --> 24:01.799
Micky, hand.

24:01.800 --> 24:03.360
Why haven't you packed yet?

24:06.320 --> 24:08.680
Can't beat a pan of scouse.

24:17.840 --> 24:19.599
Sprouts, Kell?

24:19.600 --> 24:22.159
