24:22.160 --> 24:26.839
laying on the wedding of the year's
taking its toll.

24:26.840 --> 24:27.960
(I love you.)

24:46.720 --> 24:48.799
I don't need it.

24:48.800 --> 24:50.680
Looks like someone's had a few
beers.

24:50.681 --> 24:53.960
If you want to get rid of me,
you'll have to do it your way.

25:04.520 --> 25:06.959
I've got something I need to say.

25:06.960 --> 25:10.679
I know most of you don't want
this to happen.

25:10.680 --> 25:14.760
Nice to see no one's denying it.
Appreciate the honesty.

25:16.760 --> 25:18.999
So, in case anyone gets a bit brave,

25:19.000 --> 25:23.079
"Speak now or forever
hold your peace..."

25:23.080 --> 25:25.560
I'm gonna prove
I know what I'm doing.

25:29.800 --> 25:31.600
What was always my dream?

25:33.040 --> 25:37.199
When you were kids,
where was my dream place to live?

25:37.200 --> 25:38.760
Aigburth?

25:39.960 --> 25:41.160
By the sea.

25:43.200 --> 25:47.600
The final piece in my jigsaw of life.
Keep me happy til the day I die.

26:00.640 --> 26:03.279
Three months ago your father rang me.

26:03.280 --> 26:04.200
Where is he?

26:04.201 --> 26:07.039
Working with some main
players out of Bangkok.

26:07.040 --> 26:09.119
Exporting all over the world.

26:09.120 --> 26:11.639
Hey ... we could visit.

26:11.640 --> 26:13.879
An 'oliday.

26:13.880 --> 26:16.040
You said you've always fancied
Thailand...?

26:16.041 --> 26:18.399
Lovely.

26:18.400 --> 26:22.359
This is his six bedroom house
on the beach. Four staff.

26:22.360 --> 26:24.199
Chauffeur driven Merc.

26:24.200 --> 26:26.959
He asked me to join him.

26:26.960 --> 26:30.279
Told me he'd do anything.
Totally new man ... begged me,

26:30.280 --> 26:32.319
said none of it mattered without me.

26:32.320 --> 26:35.039
Like a lottery win.

26:35.040 --> 26:36.920
Except...

26:38.000 --> 26:41.799
