26:41.800 --> 26:43.040
I don't believe you.

26:45.800 --> 26:48.320
First class. Manchester to Bangkok.

26:52.360 --> 26:55.359
This was before Billy turned up.

26:55.360 --> 26:56.719
That's the point.

26:56.720 --> 27:00.159
If I know that
I don't want that luxury

27:00.160 --> 27:02.399
and comfort for the rest
of my days,

27:02.400 --> 27:07.000
credit me with enough intelligence
to know what I do want now.

27:08.640 --> 27:10.879
We are doing this anyway.

27:10.880 --> 27:12.879
But you're my family.

27:12.880 --> 27:17.999
You're the people I want to spend
the rest of my life among.

27:18.000 --> 27:20.639
Your approval counts more than
I think you know.

27:20.640 --> 27:23.200
It won't be complete without
you behind us.

27:24.640 --> 27:28.960
If you really love me,
please give us your blessing.

27:35.760 --> 27:37.120
Fine.

27:45.040 --> 27:47.239
You'll always be my little star.

27:47.240 --> 27:50.599
Even Cilla couldn't knock
you off that pedestal.

27:50.600 --> 27:52.799
Never feel threatened.

27:52.800 --> 27:56.840
But I'd be the proudest mum in the
world if you'd agree to give me away.

28:01.680 --> 28:02.960
Eh.

28:09.600 --> 28:10.718
To Mimi and Billy...

28:10.719 --> 28:12.200
Mimi and Billy.

28:15.920 --> 28:20.559
(VOICES OUTSIDE) Keep away. Agh!
Get off you dickhead.

28:20.560 --> 28:21.840
Get here, you slag.

28:21.841 --> 28:24.719
I'll smash your head in!

28:24.720 --> 28:26.279
Aagh!

28:26.280 --> 28:27.680
SHOUTING CONTINUES

28:27.681 --> 28:30.319
SIRENS WAIL.

28:30.320 --> 28:33.119
Leave her alone!

28:33.120 --> 28:35.960
Get in there, you slag,
I'm warning you!

28:43.200 --> 28:47.040
(FRANK'S VOICE) 'We Gallaghers thrive
in this environment. Darwinian.

28:48.840 --> 28:51.040
'You and me... peas in a pod.'

29:02.960 --> 29:04.919
