29:04.920 --> 29:06.680
Nice timing. You come to console me?

29:06.681 --> 29:08.359
I'll say what I saw.

29:08.360 --> 29:11.679
Once it made the news
they get a bit keen for a scapegoat.

29:11.680 --> 29:13.799
I don't get you.

29:13.800 --> 29:17.119
