suspension's the easy option.

29:17.120 --> 29:18.839
Nothing I can do?

29:18.840 --> 29:20.840
Did it take you this long
to grow a pair?

29:23.080 --> 29:25.560
We are fucked.

29:27.160 --> 29:28.600
He says he's a 34 waist

29:28.601 --> 29:31.680
but I don't reckon he's seen his
bollocks since they dropped.

29:33.680 --> 29:34.960
There you go, "Dad."

29:37.200 --> 29:38.920
Finished?

29:48.400 --> 29:50.558
Got a couple of spares
for the derby on Saturday.

29:50.559 --> 29:51.840
Should batter them.

29:51.841 --> 29:54.119
He still seems wary.

29:54.120 --> 29:55.800
Micky freaking him out won't help.

29:58.040 --> 30:00.119
Fiance's still off his food.

30:00.120 --> 30:02.600
He must have lost a stone
with all this pressure.

30:05.800 --> 30:06.558
Yeah, yeah, yeah.

30:06.559 --> 30:07.800
Carl.

30:13.480 --> 30:15.599
No wires?

30:15.600 --> 30:16.839
Behave!

30:16.840 --> 30:18.160
Laters.

30:20.720 --> 30:21.880
Hope you don't mind me asking...

30:21.881 --> 30:22.999
Go on.

30:23.000 --> 30:24.879
My mates'd crumble. Bit young.

30:24.880 --> 30:27.040
I'm not saying you're
old, it's just you've

30:27.041 --> 30:29.199
got a bit more about
you than most people.

30:29.200 --> 30:30.678
What the fuck are you on about?

30:30.679 --> 30:32.400
Will you be my best man?

30:40.680 --> 30:41.918
Least you've got your appetite back.

30:41.919 --> 30:43.040
I'm hungry for you!

30:47.320 --> 30:49.959
We've got a bit of business
to attend to.

30:49.960 --> 30:53.079
Could use another set of hands.
You're family now.

30:53.080 --> 30:55.720
Bit of bonding will do you good.

31:15.920 --> 31:17.278
What's the business?

31:17.279 --> 31:18.038
You are.

31:18.039 --> 31:19.400
No point in hanging round.

31:25.920 --> 31:27.639
Agh! What the fuck's that?

31:27.640 --> 31:30.919
Steds.
Time to exercise those demons.

31:30.920 --> 31:33.679
Mild ones. Stop your whining.

31:33.680 --> 31:35.040
