31:35.041 --> 31:37.960
Mam won't want you looking like
a crackhead at the wedding.

31:39.600 --> 31:41.960
Ha-ha-ha! Come on, champ.

31:46.360 --> 31:51.999
Hello... Needed to swerve predators
a few million aeons ago?

31:52.000 --> 31:55.079
