32:20.440 --> 32:21.760
We need to talk properly.

32:21.761 --> 32:23.119
Tonight.

32:23.120 --> 32:24.320
Oh he's here now.

32:26.960 --> 32:28.080
Yeah.

32:30.520 --> 32:31.520
Got it.

32:34.040 --> 32:35.358
Lucky day, Carl.

32:35.359 --> 32:36.478
Collect that for Jamie?

32:36.479 --> 32:38.880
Be the easiest monkey
you've ever earnt.

32:42.160 --> 32:44.119
Tell him I'm passing.

32:44.120 --> 32:46.040
I don't think you've got a choice.

32:46.041 --> 32:48.839
Well, no offence,
that's exactly what I've got.

32:48.840 --> 32:49.999
Oh, aye?

32:50.000 --> 32:51.600
