32:55.840 --> 32:59.599
Feel free to stay mates with him if
you want, but I'm calling it a day.

32:59.600 --> 33:02.359
Who you talking to?

33:02.360 --> 33:04.959
Oh, well, As the man said...

33:04.960 --> 33:06.719
Old...

33:06.720 --> 33:07.799
young...

33:07.800 --> 33:10.120
