they shouldn't even have kids.

33:37.560 --> 33:39.679
Somebody else's.

33:39.680 --> 33:41.240
What you say?

33:42.360 --> 33:44.680
I'm going to have a baby. I'm sorry.

33:54.040 --> 33:56.799
Who?

33:56.800 --> 33:58.359
One of your regulars?

33:58.360 --> 34:00.919
Could be a one-off.

34:00.920 --> 34:02.880
Did you forget to take your tablets?

34:02.881 --> 34:05.799
Nothing's hundred percent.

34:05.800 --> 34:09.159
But the pill and a condom,
it makes the chances minute.

34:09.159 --> 34:11.918
So I'll buy a lottery ticket.
See if the luck continues.

34:11.920 --> 34:14.279
It wasn't on purpose!

34:14.280 --> 34:16.119
(SIGHS)

34:16.120 --> 34:17.880
I hate hurting you.

34:20.560 --> 34:23.159
Maybe it's what we need.

34:23.159 --> 34:24.518
Somebody else's baby?!

34:24.520 --> 34:27.559
A family.
No one needs to know it's not mine.

34:27.560 --> 34:30.079
Everyone knows you're a jaffa.
They'll slaughter you.

34:30.080 --> 34:31.840
Not if we say there's a new
discovery.

34:31.841 --> 34:33.879
Jesus, Shane!

34:33.880 --> 34:37.478
Call me a slag! Slap me,
make some fucking sense!

34:37.480 --> 34:38.879
We'll know.

34:38.880 --> 34:41.679
Kel, I don't care what anyone says.

34:41.679 --> 34:42.840
I'm losing all respect for you.

34:42.841 --> 34:44.918
Yeah, well you'll find it again.

34:44.920 --> 34:46.279
This can't go on.

34:46.280 --> 34:48.719
I can't go on. Without you.

34:48.719 --> 34:50.438
Yes you can.

34:50.440 --> 34:51.360
Kelly.

34:53.840 --> 34:57.080
I couldn't live without you.

35:01.600 --> 35:03.680
I don't know what I'd do.

35:04.960 --> 35:06.039
Please, Shane.

35:06.040 --> 35:09.199
Don't go there.

35:09.200 --> 35:11.799
You'll learn to love me again.

35:11.800 --> 35:13.680
I know you will.

35:24.080 --> 35:27.560
♪ THE JAM:
A Town Called Malice

35:34.720 --> 35:37.399
BELL RINGS

35:37.400 --> 35:41.559
♪ Stop dreaming of the quiet life cos
it's the one we'll never know... ♪

35:41.560 --> 35:44.239
Come on, Billy!
He's getting away from you! Go on!

35:44.240 --> 35:46.719
♪ ..those rosy days are few... ♪

35:46.720 --> 35:47.720
