35:47.721 --> 35:49.199
♪ And stop apologising

35:49.200 --> 35:51.279
♪ For the things you never done

35:51.280 --> 35:55.559
♪ Cos time is short and life is cruel
but it's up to us to change

35:55.560 --> 35:57.680
♪ This town called malice! ♪

36:07.520 --> 36:10.919
Taking him! You're doing it!
Go on, Billy!

36:10.920 --> 36:14.839
No, and the crowd go wild!

36:14.840 --> 36:17.520
(PANTS) Fuck!

36:20.480 --> 36:23.359
